Best Burgers in NYC! They have made history with their Guinness Shake! Its Guinness but they burn all the alcohol is burned so it safe for kids and perfect for adults! They burn their own Beef which is make this Place 10 times better! Nicest workers you'll ever meet! The Chef is the Nicest Chef you'll ever meet! Make sure to get there from 3:00 - 7:00 for the Happy Hour! $3.00 for a freaking Beer! AMAZING!!!! Sliders are $2.50!!!! Perfect for kids! Delicious Milkshakes! Has Seltzer for kids who are not allowed to drink soda! This is the perfect place to go on your trip to the East Village! 11/10!
